{
  "stem": "23428.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And, of course, no one, no one would tell us or nobody knew and we didn't know it was an extermination camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And of course, in some ways, it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mean I will get to that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I mean, I knew-- people knew that this was the line for Mauthausen, whether or not they called it out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How that news got around, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I remember, obviously, that he was lined up in the line other than ours.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother, my mother, and I, right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we traveled together in the same train compartment to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that's-- it's a considerable trip.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly, but something like maybe 6, 8 hours, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Auschwitz being very close to Poland, very close to Katowice.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the next thing we knew, of course, on the other end of the trip-- I don't think-- I don't remember anything about that trip, other than-- than having these rather friendly guards who were really, obviously, tried to calm us down for whatever reason, maybe just to make their jobs easier.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But probably what it was-- I would suspect it was-- it was really genuine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother was separated from us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My brother and I were led into a compound that had to do with taking your clothes, having your clothes taken away, disinfection, delousing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were sprayed with delousing powder.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Your hair was shorn.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You were tattooed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And of course, we hadn't shaved for quite some time, so I remember my brother and I looking at one another after we had put on these non-fitted clothes they'd thrown at us.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
